        "logic": "var calc_output = [];\n\nvar bmi = parseFloat(bmi);\nvar ast = parseFloat(ast);\nvar alt = parseFloat(alt);\nvar diabetes = parseFloat(diabetes);\n\nvar ratio = ast/alt;\n\nvar x;\n\nif (ratio >= 0.8) {\n    x = 2;\n}\nelse if (ratio < 0.8) {\n    x = 0;\n}\n\nvar score = bmi + x + diabetes; \n\nvar risk;\n\nif (score <= 1) {\n    risk = 'Low';\n}\nelse {\n    risk = 'High';\n}\n\n//results \ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'mini',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: risk +' risk'\n    });\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'score',\n    value: score,\n    value_text: 'points',\n    message: 'BARD Score'\n    });\nif (score <= 1) {\ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'risk',\n    value: risk,\n    value_text: 'risk',\n    message: ''\n    });\n}\nelse { \ncalc_output.push({\n    name: 'risk',\n    value: risk,\n    value_text: 'risk',\n    message: 'Scores 2-4 were associated with odds ratio 17 (see Evidence for details). In low risk patients (scores 0-1), consider avoiding biopsy.'\n    });\n}\n",
